CI/CD
Pipeline:
    Jenkins - pipeline for build, testing and deploy source code from GitHub
    GoCD
    GitHub Actions

        Build:
            NuGet
            MSBuild
            Maven
            Gradle

        Testing:
            XUnit
            Docker - one requirements

        Publish artifact in repository:
            aptly
            Artifactory
            Pulp
            Reposilite
            Debian Package Repository Producer
            Archiva
            Sonatype Nexus Repository OSS
            RhodeCode
            Kallithea

        Deploy:
            Ansible - install environment. Install artifact from repository
            Ansistrano



Glossary: "Artifact" is concatenate "art" + "fact". Артефакт - это "исскуство" + "факт", т.е. факт деятельности человека. Исскуство свойственно только человеку, исскуственно созданный человеком предмет.
